ores-rcfilters-ores-conflicts-logactions: Ek vo odik "Iogdanacho Gunn" vo "Vaporpeacho Hetu" gallnnent "{{int:rcfilters-filter-logactions-label}}" gallnni kijil korta. Sotran ghatlelea karia pasot Gunnache ani Hetuchem parkhop uplobdh na. Kijilacheo gallnneo Kriaxil gallnnechea kxetrant  voir khunnaileat.
ores-rcfilters-logactions-conflicts-ores: Hi gallnni ek vo odik Iogdanache Gunn vo Vaporpeachea Hetu gallnnent kijil asa. Gunnacho ani Hetuchem parkhop sotran nond kel'lea kariak uplobdh na.
ores-rcfilters-damaging-whats-this-body: Hem parkhop iontrachea xikpache seve vorvim kelam jem vhoddlea sompadonache vhodd pongodd acher proxikxonn zalam zankam monxamnim topaslam. Odik koddok, chodd ochuk gallnneank thoddem khottem hoikarponn melltta punn tanche choddxe mokh chukhta. Unnea ochuk gallnneank tanche unnem mokh mellta, punn tankam odik khottem hoikarponn-ui melltta.
ores-rcfilters-damaging-conflicts-logact: Iogdanachem Gunnachem parkhop kaim bodolache prokarank uplobdh na, hea khatir gallnnek fuddem ievpi Bodolachea Prokar {{PLURAL:$2|gallnnek|gallnenk}} kijil asa: $1
ores-rcfilters-damaging-likelygood-desc: Sogllea prosn-mekllea sompadon mellpa khatir chodd ochuk.
ores-rcfilters-damaging-maybebad-desc: Chodd chukichem vo ibadd korpi sompadonam choddxem mellttat, punn unnem ochukponnant.
ores-rcfilters-damaging-likelybad-desc-l: Modlem ochukponnant, prosnachea sompadonacho modlo kuddko melltta.
ores-rcfilters-damaging-verylikelybad-de: Chodd chukichem vo ibadd korpi sompadon sodpak chodd vhodd ochukechem.
ores-rcfilters-goodfaith-whats-this-body: Vaporpeachea hetu vixim hem parkhop iontrachea xikpache seve vorvim kelam jem vhoddlea sompadonache vhodd pongodd acher proxikxonn zalam zankam monxamnim topaslam. Odik koddok, chodd ochuk gallnneank thoddem khottem hoikarponn melltta punn tanche choddxe mokh chukhta. Unnea ochuk gallnneank tanche unnem mokh mellta, punn tankam odik khottem hoikarponn-ui melltta.
ores-rcfilters-goodfaith-conflicts-logac: Vaporpeache hetuchem poilem parkhop kaim bodlachea prokarank uplobdh na, hea khatir he gallnnek fuddem ieta tea 'Bodolacho Prokar' {{PLURAL:$2|gallnnek}} kijil asa: $1
ores-rcfilters-goodfaith-good-desc: Sogllea borea hetuchea sompadon mellpa khatir chodd ochuk.
ores-rcfilters-goodfaith-maybebad-desc: Vaitt hetuchem sompadonam choddxem mellttat, punn unnem ochukponnant.
ores-rcfilters-goodfaith-bad-desc-low: Modlem ochukponnant, vaitt hetuchea sompadonacho modlo kuddko melltta.
ores-rcfilters-goodfaith-bad-desc-high: Modlem ochukponnan choddxe vaitt hetuche sompadon mellta.
ores-rcfilters-goodfaith-verylikelybad-d: Chodd vaitt hetuchem sompadon sodpak chodd vhodd ochukechem.
